title: Scenic, 1795–1825
creditline: Gift of John Judkyn in memory of his mother, Florence Judkyn
description: Gray sky background. Bamboo trees. Large central tree with many purple blossoms. Branches, with red fruit, growing from the left. Multi-colored birds and insects. Conventionalized green ground at bottom with flowers.

tombstone.epitaph:
Scenic, 1795–1825.
1795–1825. Hand painted on handmade paper. Gift of John Judkyn in memory of his mother, Florence Judkyn. 1954-168-3.
